com.tibco.tea.agent.metrics

Interface MetricsRegistry


  • public interface MetricsRegistry
    MetricsRegistry is registry of all the metrics managed by the base agent.

    MetricsRegistry provides a series of methods for creating all the supported types of metrics. These methods create the desired metric, store the metric in the registry and then return the newly created metric.

    Example: 

     MetricsRegistry metricsRegistry = teaAgent.getMetricsRegistry();
 Counter counter = metricsRegistry.createGauge(HelloWorld.SERVER, "server1", "request-count", "Requests");
